{"tid":1800158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[自煮燃發] 中國那個將Sim卡與MicroSD卡整合在一起的「超級SIM卡」很厲害？其實你也可以自己在家DIY做一個","createTime":"2019-12-27T14:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:09:01.000Z","uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"195488f0fa2fa4e42d80f584d55c6a7004d1ff57","tid":1800158,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"前兩天中國電信公司廣州聯通和紫光國微宣布合作開發的「5G 超級 SIM 卡」上市。廠商宣稱，在一張卡上同時完成了儲存功能和 SIM 卡通訊功能。事實上，這個所謂超級SIM卡在今年五月就已經傳出，當時的確也引起了不小的轟動。不過，原本的消息是「超級SIM卡」本身會整合32GB起步的儲存空間，而且「無需儲存卡便能直接給手機擴充容量」。不過，當產品實際推出時，許多人都有種「被騙」的感覺。"},{"pid":"bfba9baf3759f5786e7805338b2839a5d0368349","tid":1800158,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"畢竟，「無需儲存卡便能直接給手機擴充容量」這句話太吸引人，難道是相關的廠商搞出了什麼黑科技，直接把 SIM卡的內置儲存空間擴大了幾萬倍？問題是 SIM卡與手機之間的觸點和應用程式介面(API)是固定的，那麼超級 SIM卡又是如何解決與手機之間硬體的問題的呢，難不成需要手機廠商使用專門改造的 SIM卡插槽嗎？<br />\n<br />\n事實證明，我們還是太傻太天真了，而相關廠商的創意程度也超乎我們的想像。究竟「5G超級SIM卡」是如何實現 SIM卡大容量內置儲存的呢？大家首先請看其官方近日發佈的「支援終端情況說明」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.36krcdn.com/20191225/v2_df88e32e60e54aaeb8cdf16d54a04b52_img_000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.36krcdn.com%2F20191225%2Fv2_df88e32e60e54aaeb8cdf16d54a04b52_img_000&h=312110b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83ea1b1ac1b6a2498820ad5c59ad937fa214632a","tid":1800158,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"看明白了嗎？如果還不明白是怎麼回事，那麼技術要點總結為了如下幾條：<br />\n<br />\n首先，「5G超級SIM卡」首先需要手機支援TF卡擴充，如果手機本身就不支援TF卡擴充，則「超級SIM卡」是不能使用的。<br />\n其次，「5G超級SIM卡」不光要求手機支援TF卡，而且還要求手機必須是採用那種第二個 SIM卡必須是和TF「二選一」的卡槽。對於更實用的雙 SIM+獨立TF卡的卡槽也不支援。<br />\n最後，按照目前官方所說的說明，「5G超級SIM卡」推薦的適配機型，居然全部都是4G手機，而且適配機型沒有一款是近代的旗艦型號，全部為中低階和老機型。<br />\n等等，事情好像哪裡不對？為什麼明明是備受期待的「5G SIM卡」，相容的卻是4G機型；為什麼自稱是大容量儲存的新型 SIM卡，可用起來卻還是要求手機首先要支援特定形狀的 TF卡槽不可呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實「5G超級SIM卡」的秘密，或許根本就沒有那麼複雜。因為早在多年之前，在某些手機論壇就教過你，你也可以自己DIY做一個。"},{"pid":"b7cf7e2e697fc2947fc963e71752918684d7e5ec","tid":1800158,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.36krcdn.com/20191225/v2_90107aeab99a4582bb01d1fb3eb1ff29_img_000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.36krcdn.com%2F20191225%2Fv2_90107aeab99a4582bb01d1fb3eb1ff29_img_000&h=b7f9dfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這樣的成果：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.36krcdn.com/20191225/v2_abc85a5608ee49ce8a4af438cb6472c2_img_000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.36krcdn.com%2F20191225%2Fv2_abc85a5608ee49ce8a4af438cb6472c2_img_000&h=4231dd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝進手機卡槽之後是這樣的：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.36krcdn.com/20191225/v2_33a8a0c8c10c48e39e991d56a8fa4e1a_img_000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.36krcdn.com%2F20191225%2Fv2_33a8a0c8c10c48e39e991d56a8fa4e1a_img_000&h=44e9a2f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abd55c491bd92af008a0c553bdb325f26ec1edf5","tid":1800158,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"沒錯，大家可能已經看明白是怎麼一回事了，其實就是把傳統的 SIM卡晶片摳出來，再把 TF卡有觸點的那一面打磨出一個小坑，然後再把 SIM卡直接粘進去。由於手機卡槽實際上具備 SIM卡和 TF卡兩套位置不衝突的觸點，因此這種強行改造的「TF+ SIM二合一卡」就可以被分別認成一張 SIM卡和一張 TF卡，並且能夠同時使用。<br />\n<br />\n當然，嚴格來說，以上所說的所有的都只是技術層面上的推測。畢竟「5G超級SIM卡」的官方至今也沒有放出其產品觸點那一面的實拍圖像，因此暫時還沒辦法直接證實這一猜測。但問題就來了，「5G超級SIM卡」背面的造型現在是已經公開了的&mdash;&mdash;大家自己看覺得這像什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.36krcdn.com/20191225/v2_563c74e234ae4f47aaef81424eede06c_img_000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.36krcdn.com%2F20191225%2Fv2_563c74e234ae4f47aaef81424eede06c_img_000&h=7f5e7f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，64GB的「5G超級 SIM卡」要價199元（人民幣），而目前市面上一線大廠 TF卡同等容量的價格卻僅要39-49元（人民幣），這中間的差價又是怎麼一回事呢？<br />\n<br />\nReference: <a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/75283-chinas-super-sim-card-appears-really-not-sim-card-and-tf-together\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F75283-chinas-super-sim-card-appears-really-not-sim-card-and-tf-together&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPE4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=1625b561\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/75283-chinas-super-sim-card-appears-really-not-sim-card-and-tf-together</a>"},{"pid":"c26a023f598b183678f01aaa0f7093c90fc900fe","tid":1800158,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.clubsim.com.hk/clsecomm/supersimselection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clubsim.com.hk%2Fclsecomm%2Fsupersimselection&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPE4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=54120c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clubsim.com.hk/clsecomm/supersimselection</a><br />\n同依個有咩分別？"},{"pid":"d0dc8b7dbf59a02cd45b29505134cf275ffa282f","tid":1800158,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c26a023f598b183678f01aaa0f7093c90fc900fe","tid":1800158,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.clubsim.com.hk/clsecomm/supersimselection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clubsim.com.hk%2Fclsecomm%2Fsupersimselection&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPE4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=54120c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clubsim.com.hk/clsecomm/supersimselection</a><br />\n同依個有咩分別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />5G"},{"pid":"4fb2fe3b358d65a4ac344a6c6991c552c8178d62","tid":1800158,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c26a023f598b183678f01aaa0f7093c90fc900fe","tid":1800158,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.clubsim.com.hk/clsecomm/supersimselection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clubsim.com.hk%2Fclsecomm%2Fsupersimselection&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPE4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=54120c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clubsim.com.hk/clsecomm/supersimselection</a><br />\n同依個有咩分別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"分別在於自煮燃發"}]}